{
  "stem": "21786.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyhow, within the next 20 minutes, I let her know about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I must say one thing, that from that moment on, nothing was ever reported.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did awful breaks of rules.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were getting bread and we were getting margarine and all kinds of stuff from these women.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would deny everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would always, when some of the key SS men would come with us, so they would take him inside of the laundry and I just got an echo.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to the thermostat-- a primitive kind of thermostat-- and we raised the heat to the top.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were working half naked, which the SS men liked, but they have been in felt uniform and they lasted about five minutes and they were out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I had three free days of-- for this went only for three days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I became a servant for the leadership-- prisoner leadership of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were three Germans-- I mean Aryan Germans-- who were in the main camp since 1933.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was their 12th year-- 11th and 12th year in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were imprisoned as Communist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were straight like a line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Very strict.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they were fellow prisoners, and they fought for us tooth and nail.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they, for instance, if somebody would be caught stealing somebody's piece of bread, so they would rip him bad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On the other hand, if the SS men would catch him to do something that he would be hanged, they talked him out of it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they were Germans, and they could afford, I mean, to talk to the SS men, like, completely on a different level.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
